   [nasaball_medium.gif] The aeronautical and space activities of the
   United States shall be conducted so as to contribute... to the
   expansion of human knowledge of phenomena in the atmosphere and space.
   The Administration shall provide for the widest practicable and
   appropriate dissemination of information concerning its activities and
   the results thereof.

   -- National Aeronautics and Space Act of 1958
